1. You must have node.js to use Node Based JavaScript
   on your System.
2. run the command in this folder "npm install" and all the
   dependencies will be installed
3. Make a shortcut of the file "[BOOT SLIMESHELL]" in the
   startup folder and move it to whereever you want.
4. Run your new shortcut "[BOOT SLIMESHELL]" and it will start
   electron running SlimeShell!
5. Enjoy Customizing your new Shell Like Desktop Interface!
